title: LaSalle's Gimbel Seeing No Signs of Slowdown for Hiring (Audio)

(Bloomberg) -- Taking Stock with Kathleen Hays and Pimm Fox. GUEST: National labor market expert, Tom Gimbel, founder & CEO of LaSalle Network, looks ahead to jobs day, weighing in on hiring trends and health of the market.
